oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Gay Street
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Gay Street looking north, Knoxville, TN. United Shoe Hospital, Chambers Real Estate Insurance Loans at left. Sterchi Bros. in center background. Szabo, Askin-Martin, Spence Shoe Company, Farragut Hotel, Tennessee Theatre, S&W Cafeteria, Bankers Trust Company, The Knoxville Journal, Post Sign Co., Original Sandwich Shop, May Drug Co. at right. Streetcar and cars on street.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Streets; Street railroads; Business enterprises; Automobiles; Motion picture theaters; Cafeterias; Banks; Newspaper industry;
